        "comment": {
            "name": "comment",
            "type": "com.atlassian.jira.issue.fields.CommentSystemField",
            "value": [
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/39738",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "How do you call Zend_Translate ?\r\nWe need some information for a reproduction.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-04-02T05:49:03.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-04-02T05:49:03.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/39785",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=back-2-95",
                        "name": "back-2-95",
                        "displayName": "Marko Korhonen",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I use ini file with Zend_Application, so it uses Translation resource:\r\n\r\nhere's my translate from ini file:\r\nresources.translate.adapter = array\r\nresources.translate.locale = fi_FI\r\nresources.translate.data = APPLICATION_PATH \"\/translations\"\r\nresources.translate.options.scan = directory\r\nresources.translate.options.logUntranslated = false\r\n\r\nadditionally, I load module specific translations in my Bootstrap:\r\n\r\npublic function _initTranslateModuleLoader()\r\n\t{\r\n\t\t$this->bootstrap(array(\"locale\", \"translate\"));\r\n\r\n\t\t$translate = $this->getResource(\"translate\");\r\n\t\t$locale = $this->getResource(\"locale\");\r\n\r\n\t\tforeach ($this->modules as $module => $directory)\r\n\t\t{\r\n\t\t\t$translation_file = dirname($directory) .\"\/translations\/{$locale->toString()}.php\";\r\n\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\tif (file_exists($translation_file))\r\n\t\t\t{\r\n\t\t\t\trequire_once($translation_file);\r\n\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\tif (isset($translations) && is_array($translations))\r\n\t\t\t\t{\r\n\t\t\t\t\t$translate->addTranslation($translations);\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\tunset($translations);\r\n\t\t\t\t}\r\n\t\t\t}\r\n\t\t}\r\n\t}",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=back-2-95",
                        "name": "back-2-95",
                        "displayName": "Marko Korhonen",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-04-04T03:29:15.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-04-04T03:29:15.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/39836",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Fixed with r21770.\r\n\r\nNote that the problem is related to Zend_Application_Ressource_Translate which you are using and not within Zend_Translate.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-04-05T13:17:35.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-04-05T13:17:35.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/39904",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=hendri.smit",
                        "name": "hendri.smit",
                        "displayName": "Hendri Smit",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I use the following configuration:\r\n\r\n{code:xml}\r\nresources.translate.adapter = csv\r\nresources.translate.data = APPLICATION_PATH \"\/languages\/nl.csv\"\r\nresources.translate.locale = \"nl\"\r\n{code}\r\n\r\nThis results in (with and without the changes in r21770):\r\n{color:red}\r\nFatal error: Uncaught exception 'Zend_Translate_Exception' with message 'Error opening translation file 'Array'\r\n{color}\r\n",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=hendri.smit",
                        "name": "hendri.smit",
                        "displayName": "Hendri Smit",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-04-09T06:50:53.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-04-09T06:50:53.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/39906",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I don't understand what this has to do with this issue.\r\nHere is a problem described with raised notices.\r\n\r\nYou mention a problem where Zend_Translate returns that a file can not be opened. And you are using a different configuration as the reporter of this issue.\r\n\r\nPlease note that different issues should not be thrown together into one.\r\n\r\nFor default problems like described by you, please ask within our mailinglist or within our IRC channel.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-04-09T08:08:25.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-04-09T08:08:25.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/39917",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=hendri.smit",
                        "name": "hendri.smit",
                        "displayName": "Hendri Smit",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "After reading this issue I thought r21770 was supposed to fix problems between the improved Zend_Translate and Zend_Application_Resource_Translate.\r\n\r\nI'm currently running a site on ZF 1.10.2 with the configuration I mentioned and without any problems.\r\nAfter upgrading to ZF 1.10.3 I got the Fatal error. I thought it had something to do with this issue.\r\n\r\nI then applied the changes in r21770 but that didn't solve anything. So I assumed the changes you made weren't sufficient.\r\nThat was a wrong assumption. Sorry for that.\r\n\r\nToday I tried upgrading again and now the errors don't appear. So I probably made a mistake yesterday while doing the upgrade.\r\n\r\nYou're probably right that it would have been better to create a new issue. But next time I'll first make sure it's not me being stupid ;)",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=hendri.smit",
                        "name": "hendri.smit",
                        "displayName": "Hendri Smit",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-04-10T04:06:08.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-04-10T04:06:08.000+0000"
                }
            ]
        }
